content.text: This is a 512*512 remote sensing image for uav navigation.The red circle marks the starting point, the yellow circle marks the destination, blue dots (or rectangles) indicate must-pass waypoints (or regions), and green dots (or rectangles) represent no-fly points (or regions). Please provide a valid and feasible path in the format: [(x1, y1), (x2, y2), ..., (xn, yn)].
